                  </persName>
            , <rs id="t18020428-23-viclabel121" type="occupation">widow</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020428-23-victim201 t18020428-23-viclabel121"></join>.(The prisoner being a foreigner, a Jury of half foreigners were sworn.)</p>
         
